# AntiGravity AI Script Agent — CV Forge

## PROJECT CONTEXT

Nama project: CV Forge
Framework: Next.js 16 App Router
Frontend: React 19 + TypeScript
Styling: TailwindCSS v4 + shadcn/ui
Animation: Framer Motion
State Management: Zustand
PDF/Image Export:

* jspdf
* html2canvas
* html-to-image

Payment Gateway:

* PayPal
* Midtrans

Deployment:

* Vercel

Target aplikasi:
CV Forge adalah AI-powered resume / CV builder berbasis web yang memungkinkan user:

* membuat CV ATS-friendly
* export PDF
* custom template
* generate CV dengan AI
* save draft
* melakukan pembayaran premium
* menggunakan template modern
* melakukan export image / pdf
* monetisasi dengan ads dan premium plan

---

# TECH STACK

## Core

* Next.js 16.2.6
* React 19.2.4
* TypeScript 5

## UI

* TailwindCSS v4
* shadcn/ui
* Base UI
* Lucide React
* Framer Motion

## Utility

* clsx
* class-variance-authority
* tailwind-merge

## State

* Zustand

## Export

* html2canvas
* html-to-image
* jspdf

## Payment

* Midtrans
* PayPal

## Deployment

* Vercel

