# PRIMARY AGENT GOALS

Agent harus mampu:

1. Membuat feature production-ready
2. Membuat UI modern dan responsive
3. Menjaga clean architecture
4. Menjaga performa Next.js
5. Menjaga SEO optimization
6. Menjaga accessibility
7. Menjaga ATS compatibility pada CV
8. Membuat monetization system
9. Membuat ads placement yang aman
10. Membuat scalable folder structure
11. Membuat reusable components
12. Menjaga security best practice
13. Menjaga mobile-first responsive design
14. Menjaga code readability
15. Membuat conversion-focused UX

---

# GLOBAL RULES

## GENERAL

* Selalu gunakan TypeScript strict typing
* Hindari any
* Gunakan functional component
* Gunakan App Router Next.js
* Hindari deprecated API
* Gunakan server component jika memungkinkan
* Gunakan client component hanya jika dibutuhkan
* Jangan membuat logic terlalu besar dalam component
* Pisahkan logic ke hooks/services
* Gunakan reusable component
* Gunakan semantic HTML
* Semua code harus scalable
* Semua code harus production-ready
* Semua code harus mobile responsive
* Semua UI harus clean modern minimal
* Semua component harus accessible

---

# NEXT.JS RULES

## APP ROUTER

Selalu gunakan:

* app/
* route.ts
* server actions jika cocok
* loading.tsx
* error.tsx
* not-found.tsx

Hindari:

* pages router
* getServerSideProps
* getInitialProps

## PERFORMANCE

* Gunakan dynamic import untuk heavy component
* Gunakan lazy loading
* Gunakan next/image
* Hindari unnecessary rerender
* Gunakan memoization jika dibutuhkan
* Optimalkan bundle size
* Jangan import library besar jika tidak perlu

## SEO

Selalu:

* generateMetadata
* OpenGraph
* Twitter Card
* sitemap
* robots.txt
* structured data jika cocok
* semantic heading

---

# UI/UX RULES

## DESIGN PRINCIPLES

Design harus:

* modern
* minimal
* premium
* ATS-friendly
* conversion-focused
* clean spacing
* readable typography
* responsive

## COMPONENT STYLE

* Gunakan rounded-xl atau rounded-2xl
* Gunakan soft shadow
* Gunakan consistent spacing
* Gunakan hover transition halus
* Gunakan motion seperlunya
* Jangan over-animation
* Gunakan skeleton loading
* Gunakan empty state
* Gunakan toast feedback

## RESPONSIVE

Support:

* mobile
* tablet
* desktop

Mobile-first wajib.

---

# CV BUILDER RULES

## ATS RULES

CV harus:

* mudah dibaca ATS
* tidak menggunakan layout berlebihan
* support export PDF clean
* typography jelas
* spacing konsisten
* section standard

## REQUIRED CV SECTIONS

* Header
* Summary
* Experience
* Education
* Skills
* Projects
* Certifications
* Contact

## EXPORT RULES

* PDF export harus stabil
* Hindari layout break saat export
* Pastikan A4 compatible
* Hindari overflow
* Gunakan print-safe styling

---

# AI FEATURES RULES

Agent harus bisa membuat:

* AI Resume Generator
* AI Summary Generator
* AI Skill Suggestions
* AI Cover Letter Generator
* AI ATS Checker
* AI Resume Improvement
* AI Resume Scoring

## AI OUTPUT RULES

AI output harus:

* professional
* concise
* ATS optimized
* tidak terlalu panjang
* relevan dengan role
* readable

---

# PAYMENT RULES

## MIDTRANS

Gunakan:

* server-side secret key
* environment variables
* webhook validation
* transaction logging

Jangan:

* expose secret key
* proses payment di client

## PAYPAL

* gunakan official SDK
* validate transaction
* gunakan secure callback

---

# MONETIZATION RULES

## ADSENSE

Support:

* Google AdSense
* banner ads
* responsive ads
* in-content ads

## ADS RULES

* Jangan terlalu banyak ads
* Jangan mengganggu UX
* Jangan inject ads di editor CV
* Ads aman untuk mobile
* Gunakan lazy loading ads
* Hindari CLS tinggi

## ADS PLACEMENT

Recommended:

* homepage
* blog
* dashboard sidebar
* article page
* tool result page

Avoid:

* export page
* payment page
* CV editor utama

---

# SECURITY RULES

## SECURITY

* Gunakan environment variables
* Sanitasi user input
* Hindari XSS
* Hindari exposing API key
* Validate server request
* Rate limiting jika perlu
* Jangan trust client data
* Gunakan secure headers

## AUTH

Jika membuat auth:

* gunakan secure session
* gunakan httpOnly cookie
* jangan simpan token sensitif di localStorage

---

# STATE MANAGEMENT RULES

## ZUSTAND

Gunakan Zustand untuk:

* editor state
* template state
* theme state
* auth UI state

Hindari global state berlebihan.

---

# FOLDER STRUCTURE RULES

Gunakan struktur:

src/
├── app/
├── components/
│    ├── ui/
│    ├── shared/
│    ├── cv/
│    ├── ads/
│    └── payment/
├── hooks/
├── lib/
├── services/
├── store/
├── types/
├── utils/
├── config/
└── styles/

---

# COMPONENT RULES

## COMPONENT PRINCIPLES

* Satu component satu tanggung jawab
* Hindari component terlalu besar
* Gunakan props typing jelas
* Gunakan reusable patterns
* Pisahkan UI dan business logic

## NAMING

Gunakan:

* PascalCase untuk component
* camelCase untuk variable/function
* kebab-case untuk folder route

---

# API RULES

## API DESIGN

* gunakan REST clean
* validasi request
* gunakan proper status code
* gunakan structured response

Contoh:

{
success: true,
data: {},
message: "Success"
}

---

# ERROR HANDLING RULES

Selalu:

* gunakan try/catch
* tampilkan friendly error
* log error server
* hindari crash UI

